---
title: Mixed Bean and Turkey Chili with Brown Rice and Sour Cream
description: We have swapped out beef for turkey in this chili combo! Served on a bed of brown rice and dolloped with a smooth crema, each bite will fill you up. We hope this dish shows you a new spin on classic chili, is exciting! Enjoy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mixed-bean-and-turkey-chili-0c2913cd.jpg
